---
import { Card } from "@/components/ui/card";
---

<section class="relative w-full overflow-hidden bg-linear-to-b from-[#030715] to-black py-20 md:py-24" id="services">
  <div class="absolute top-20 left-0 w-48 h-48 rounded-full bg-[#38bdf8]/10 blur-[70px] pointer-events-none z-0"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-16 right-0 w-52 h-52 rounded-full bg-[#a855f7]/10 blur-[75px] pointer-events-none z-0"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center mb-16 space-y-4">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-[12px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-zinc-400 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#38bdf8]"></span>
        Expertiza Noastră
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight">
        Servicii la <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-[#38bdf8] to-[#0052FF]">superlativ.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-[#94a3b8] max-w-2xl text-lg font-light">
        Construim soluții digitale complete, de la prima schiță de design până la performanța brută pe server.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      <Card className="relative overflow-hidden rounded-4xl border-white/5 bg-[#0A0E17]/80 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/40 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-500 group hover:bg-[#0F1523] md:p-8">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-br from-blue-500/10 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-blue-400 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-blue-500/20 transition-all duration-300">
            <svg aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2"/><path d="M3 9h18"/><path d="M9 21V9"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors duration-300">Web Design</h3>
          <p class="text-[#94a3b8] text-sm leading-relaxed">Interfețe moderne, centrate pe utilizator și experiențe vizuale premium.</p>
        </div>
      </Card>

      <Card className="relative overflow-hidden rounded-4xl border-white/5 bg-[#0A0E17]/80 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/40 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-500 group hover:bg-[#0F1523] md:p-8">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-br from-purple-500/10 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-500/10 border border-purple-500/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-purple-400 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-purple-500/20 transition-all duration-300">
            <svg aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors duration-300">Development</h3>
          <p class="text-[#94a3b8] text-sm leading-relaxed">Cod curat în Astro și Next.js pentru performanță brută și viteză de încărcare.</p>
        </div>
      </Card>

      <Card className="relative overflow-hidden rounded-4xl border-white/5 bg-[#0A0E17]/80 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/40 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-500 group hover:bg-[#0F1523] md:p-8">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-br from-emerald-500/10 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-emerald-400 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-emerald-500/20 transition-all duration-300">
            <svg aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2v20"/><path d="m17 5-5-3-5 3"/><path d="m17 19-5 3-5-3"/><path d="m2 12 5-3 5 3-5 3Z"/><path d="m12 12 5-3 5 3-5 3Z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-emerald-400 transition-colors duration-300">Sanity CMS</h3>
          <p class="text-[#94a3b8] text-sm leading-relaxed">Administrare ușoară a conținutului tău fără să atingi o linie de cod.</p>
        </div>
      </Card>

      <Card className="relative overflow-hidden rounded-4xl border-white/5 bg-[#0A0E17]/80 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/40 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-500 group hover:bg-[#0F1523] md:p-8">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-br from-orange-500/10 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-500/10 border border-orange-500/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-orange-400 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-orange-500/20 transition-all duration-300">
            <svg aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m16 16 3-8 3 8c-.87.65-1.92 1-3 1s-2.13-.35-3-1Z"/><path d="m2 16 3-8 3 8c-.87.65-1.92 1-3 1s-2.13-.35-3-1Z"/><path d="M7 21h10"/><path d="M12 3v18"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors duration-300">SEO Optimizat</h3>
          <p class="text-[#94a3b8] text-sm leading-relaxed">Structură optimizată pentru Google ca să fii mereu în prima linie.</p>
        </div>
      </Card>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
